#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "GatherPress References"
msgstr "GatherPress Referenzen"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Display references such as clients, festivals and awards in a structured, "
"chronological format."
msgstr ""
"Referenzen wie Auftraggeber, Festivals und Auszeichnungen in einem "
"strukturierten, chronologischen Format anzeigen."

